  "detailed_description": "<strong>Test your survival skill</strong><br>The game consists of independent scenarios united by a common event that led to the end of humanity, try to get out of this situation and reach the end.<br><br><strong>Intuitive interaction with the environment</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/eb0bb68dc07a42110688b9ee7f672694.poster.avif?t=1746603450\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/eb0bb68dc07a42110688b9ee7f672694.webm?t=1746603450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/eb0bb68dc07a42110688b9ee7f672694.mp4?t=1746603450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/e7e05234a0e8ea5458c3376fb583952b.poster.avif?t=1746603450\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/e7e05234a0e8ea5458c3376fb583952b.webm?t=1746603450\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/e7e05234a0e8ea5458c3376fb583952b.mp4?t=1746603450\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Gun porn element with quality physics</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/7530003b5400f7e2bd292139fb1536d3.poster.avif?t=1746603450\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885820/extras/7530003b5400f7e2bd292139fb1536d3.webm